<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">A 3,200-year saga of genetic memory and hidden knowledge</p>
    <h1>The Architecture of Survival</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Twelve books spanning Bronze Age Egypt to the AI era, following two competing networks
      locked in an existential conflict over humanity's survival. What if genetic memory is real?
      What if civilizational collapse is preventable—or inevitable?
    </p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="button" href="/books/">Explore the 12 books</a>
      <a class="button ghost" href="/series/">About the saga</a>
    </div>
    <div class="meta">
      <span>3,200 years | 138 generations | 12 books</span>
      <span>~900,000 words when complete</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-card reveal delay-1">
    <div class="cover">
      <img
        src="/assets/book-cover.webp"
        alt="The Aethelred Cipher book cover"
