        <span class="rating-text">4.8 out of 5 &mdash; <a href="/reviews.html">56 ratings on Amazon</a></span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-actions">
        <a class="text-link" href="/books/#book1">See details</a>
        <a class="text-link" href="{{ site.amazonUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buy now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section grounds-hero-cta">
  <div class="grounds-hero-banner reveal">
    <div class="grounds-hero-banner-text">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--accent);">Interactive Experience</p>
      <h2>Let AI Read Your Coffee Grounds</h2>
      <p>
        In <em>The Genesis Protocol</em>, a pattern hiding in coffee residue held a message no one was meant to find.
        The ancient art of tasseography reveals what's left behind &mdash; patterns invisible to everyone except those trained to look.
      </p>
      <p class="grounds-hero-banner-sub">Upload a photo of your cup. See what the grounds reveal about your week ahead.</p>
      <a class="button" href="/read-your-grounds.html" style="background: var(--accent); margin-top: 8px;">Read Your Grounds &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grounds-hero-banner-visual">
      <span class="grounds-symbol">&#9752;</span>
    </div>
  </div>
