        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="book-status">📖 Published | ~78,000 words</div>
        <h3>Book 1: The Aethelred Cipher</h3>
        <p class="book-period">Medieval Germany, 1347-1350 CE</p>
        <p class="social-proof">4.8 stars from 56 ratings on Amazon</p>
        <p>
          When a dying monk thrusts an iron key into scribe Thomas's hands, he inherits
          more than an artifact—he becomes the target of a millennia-old conspiracy. The
          Black Death rages, and the Order has been engineering bloodlines for over 900 years.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button outline" href="/books/#book1">Read more</a>
          <a class="button ghost" href="{{ site.amazonUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buy now</a>
        </div>
