    <article class="book-card reveal delay-2">
      <div class="book-cover">
        <img src="/assets/book2-cover.webp" alt="The Genesis Protocol" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="book-status">📖 Published | ~75,000 words</div>
        <h3>Book 2: The Genesis Protocol</h3>
        <p class="book-period">Modern Era, 2019-2025 CE</p>
        <p>
          When geneticist Sarah Chen discovers an engineered bioweapon hidden inside GenVault Corporation,
          she has forty-three seconds to escape the building. What follows is a race against a
          three-thousand-year-old conspiracy, a classified pandemic, and the impossible math of silence.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button outline" href="/books/#book2">Read more</a>
          <a class="button" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GPM973N1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get on Amazon &rarr;</a>
