    </article>

    <article class="book-card reveal delay-2">
      <div class="book-cover">
        <img src="/assets/book3-cover.png" alt="The First Key book cover" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="book-status">📖 Available April 15, 2026 | ~65,000 words</div>
        <h3>Book 3: The First Key</h3>
        <p class="book-period">Bronze Age Egypt to Classical Athens, 1177-323 BCE</p>
        <p>
          The Bronze Age is collapsing. Egyptian physician Nefertari sees the pattern no one else
          does — and creates a protocol to prevent it from happening again. But her colleague
          Amenhotep sees the same evidence and reaches the opposite conclusion. Their split creates
          two networks that will chase each other through 3,200 years of history.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button outline" href="/books/#book3">Read more</a>
          <a class="button" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GSWLM1WV" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pre-order on Amazon &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
